  "remarks": "As the chairman of the Constitutional Court, he is responsible for the Constitutional Court’s decision adopted on 25 Aug 2020, by which the results of the fraudulent elections were legitimised. He has therefore supported and facilitated actions of repression and intimidation campaign by the State apparatus against peaceful protestors and journalists and is therefore responsible for seriously undermining democracy and the rule of law in Belarus.",
